<br>
That article above tells us that Shrub(Bush Jr.) is pushing to change the law<br>
from making the companies that pollute pay for the cleanups, to making US<br>
pay for the cleanups. Further, he intends to take the Superfund, and use it<br>
to featherbed. Considering that 25% of the USA citizens all live within one mile<br>
of a superfund site, that means that it DOES affect you. Like it or not.<br>
<br>
Frankly I think that is outrageous, making the victims pay for the cleanup.<br>
But it is your world that you will inherit. So I genuinely hope that you will<br>
at least think about this issue.<br>
